parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the door to lock or unlock unexpectedly, making it difficult or impossible to enter or exit the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The door locks or unlocks unexpectedly
the door does not open from the inside or outside
the door only opens from one side
the door locks or unlocks repeatedly
the door does not respond to the key fob or key.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock mechanism can cause the driver or passengers to become trapped in the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries in emergency situations.
symptoms: The door will not open from the inside or outside
the door lock will not unlock
the door handle will not operate
and the door may stick or jam.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various components to malfunction, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on
the headlights or taillights fail to work
the power windows or locks malfunction
and the electrical system may cause the vehicle to stall or lose power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on
the airbag may not deploy in an accident
and the seat belt may not retract properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the airbag light staying on, indicating a potential malfunction, which can cause the airbags to not deploy in the event of an accident, putting occupants at risk of injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag light stays on
the airbag light flickers
the airbag light comes on intermittently
the airbag light remains on after repair
the airbag does not deploy in an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Driver's Side Door Locking Mechanism Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the driver's side door locking mechanism can prevent the door from opening, potentially trapping the driver inside the vehicle, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or even fatalities in emergency situations.
symptoms: The driver's side door will not open from the inside or outside
the door lock does not respond to the key or key fob
the door lock is stuck
the door handle does not work

rusting of the door handles
